title: The Beatles Sgt. Pepper's Lonely Hearts Club Band (ORIGINAL M
description:
Holy Smokes! The original mono mix ripped @ 192.
Hard to believe that the Beatles actually first mixed Sgt. Pepper in Mono.
Stereo was still a fad and the norm was mono. It&#039;s is also hard to believe
that the mono version has not been issued via CD.
Enjoy!
